---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2026-06-18';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — health4.ai"
  description="Terms governing use of the health4.ai service."
>
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <a href="/" class="text-green-400 font-bold text-lg tracking-tight hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">health4.ai</a>
  </nav>

  <main class="px-6 py-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-sm">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-10">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      By using health4.ai ("Service"), you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, don't use the Service.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">1. What health4.ai is</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        health4.ai is a free iOS app that syncs Apple HealthKit data to a private cloud database and exposes it to AI agents (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, and others) via MCP.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-3 font-medium text-amber-300/80">
        health4.ai is not a medical device. It is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease or health condition. Do not use it to make medical decisions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">2. Acceptable use</h2>
      <ul class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-none pl-0">
        <li>You may not use health4.ai for illegal purposes, to circumvent Apple's HealthKit terms, or to process health data belonging to others without their explicit consent.</li>
        <li>We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms, with notice where possible.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">3. Your data</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        You own your health data. We store it on your behalf to provide the Service. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for full detail on how it is handled, retained, and deleted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">4. HIPAA</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        health4.ai is not a HIPAA-covered entity and does not enter into Business Associate Agreements unless separately negotiated in writing.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">5. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, health4.ai is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service, including any reliance on health data it surfaces.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">6. Changes</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        We may update these terms. Material changes will be communicated to users by email at least 14 days before taking effect.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-white font-semibold text-base mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Questions: <a href="mailto:hello@health4.ai" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">hello@health4.ai</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-neutral-800/60 px-6 py-8 mt-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-neutral-600 text-xs">
      <span>© 2026 health4.ai · Not a medical device</span>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/jefflitt1/health4ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-neutral-400 transition-colors">GitHub →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
